Not a day goes by

7
00:01:39.360 --> 00:01:40.230
that I'm not grateful.

8
00:01:40.404 --> 00:01:43.320
I mean. I mean to my bones

9
00:01:44.974 --> 00:01:46.584
about how my life turned around.

10
