00:15:49.470 --> 00:15:50.558
However you wanna do that.

277
00:15:50.732 --> 00:15:52.299
I do it kinda messy. but some people...

278
00:15:56.694 --> 00:15:59.001
Kay. thank you for tonight.

279
00:16:01.047 --> 00:16:02.135
